    <p>LON­DON • Tot­ten­ham have agreed a deal in prin­ci­ple with Southamp­ton to sign Den­mark mid­fielder Pierre-Emile Ho­jb­jerg, 25, with Kyle Walker-Pe­ters go­ing the other way, Sky Sports re­ported on Tues­day.</p>
    <p>Former Saints cap­tain Ho­jb­jerg is set to move for a fee of around £15 mil­lion (S$27 mil­lion), while 23-year-old de­fender Walker-Pe­ters, who ar­rived at St Mary’s on loan in Jan­uary, will make a per­ma­nent switch for £12 mil­lion.</p>


